long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Start n8n worflows directly from the browser. Display the information you need from any webhook. n8n extension for Chrome. 

Steps to use the chrome extension : 
1. Create a workflow
2. Add a Workflow name and your Webhook URL from n8n
3. Open your new folder add your inputs 
4. Push the data to your webhook
5. Then make your own mix in n8n
